    <briefdescription>
<para>One composer segment: a <computeroutput>synth</computeroutput> config + on/off sample counts. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The nine synth fields mirror <computeroutput><ref refid="synth__core_8h_1ab624764cabe47da500b6ddd16abe96c4" kindref="member">synth_create()</ref></computeroutput> exactly. <computeroutput><ref refid="structwfm__segment__t_1a0257700d526e5e887e192ddcbdd8a53b" kindref="member">num_samples</ref></computeroutput> is the on-time (samples emitted from the synth); <computeroutput><ref refid="structwfm__segment__t_1a67aaefb7026f996e70af85051eef365f" kindref="member">off_samples</ref></computeroutput> is a trailing gap of zeros inserted after the segment (off-time). Durations in seconds are <computeroutput>round(duration * fs)</computeroutput> — the caller resolves them. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
